by nicolas-grekas at 2019-02-23T16:49:13Z

> I would remove the possibility to serialize a Kernel as I don't see (anymore) the use cases.

Actually, that's not possible: the kernel is serialized in FrameworkBundle for insulated tests, see https://github.com/symfony/symfony/blob/3895acd17598520682468ff1aa0994b7cfc1e316/src/Symfony/Bundle/FrameworkBundle/Client.php#L164
